4. PRO LICENSE / FEATURE GATING
================================================================================
The Software is offered under a freemium model. The free tier provides the
complete core playback experience. Certain "Pro" features are unlocked with a
one-time, Ed25519-signed license key validated offline. A Pro key authorizes
use of Pro features by the licensed user; it does not expand any of the rights
restricted by Section 3, and it may not be shared, resold, or redistributed.

